Chapter.Section:
Examples Section

This worksheet exercises example and log commands in plain-text mode.



Tested examples


gap> plain_example_value := 2 + 3;
5





gap> plain_alias_example := 3 + 4;
7





gap> 10 - 3;
7





gap> 6 * 7;
42







Untested logs


gap> plain_log_value := 9;
9





gap> plain_alias_log := 11;
11





gap> "plain log session";
"plain log session"





gap> "plain alias log session";
"plain alias log session"
